 d to:\n\n✅ Provide guidance and background information on the migration\
 n\n✅ Share practical tips and best practices\n\n✅ Answer your question
 s live\n\n✅ Learn from real use cases and experiences from the community
 \n\n \n\n👥 Who should join?\n\nAnyone affected by or interested in the 
 IT migration – regardless of role or level of experience.\n\n \n\n🎙 H
 osts:\n\nCarsten & Günter\n\n \n\n📅 Format:\n\nInteractive learning & 
 Q&A sessions\n\n(Details on dates\, times\, and dial‑in will be shared i
 n this channel.) \n\n \n\n👉 Bring your questions\, challenges\, and exp
 eriences.\n\n \n\nOur goal is to learn together and support each other thr
 oughout the migration.\n\nWe’re looking forward to your participation!\n
 \nCarsten & Guenter\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n____________________________________
